---
title: Smoky Black Bean Cakes with Avocado Salsa and Tangy Arugula Salad
description: Sweet corn and creamy black beans form the base of these smoky, faintly spicy cakes. A crispy outside and soft inside give them the perfect textural contrast. Essentially a deconstructed guacamole, this avocado salsa has been deemed the king of all salsas. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56d6f5f54dab71f25a8b4567.jpg
